BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 598.0 Td (Owner: Chief Procurement Officer) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 574.0 Td (1. PURPOSE) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 558.0 Td (This policy governs the selection of suppliers for all purchase requisitions. It) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 542.0 Td (defines the preferred vendor programme, vendor qualification criteria, and the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 526.0 Td (consequences of using non-preferred suppliers.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 502.0 Td (2. PREFERRED VENDOR PROGRAMME) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 478.0 Td (2.1 Definition) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 462.0 Td (A preferred vendor is a supplier that has been qualified through the vendor) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 446.0 Td (assessment process, signed a framework agreement with standard payment terms) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 430.0 Td (\(NET30\), and demonstrated on-time delivery performance above 95% over the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 414.0 Td (preceding 12 months.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 390.0 Td (2.2 Current Preferred Vendors) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 374.0 Td (The current list of preferred vendors is maintained in the procurement system. As) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 358.0 Td (of the effective date, preferred vendors include: Apex Industrial Supplies \(V-1\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 342.0 Td (and Precision Parts Ltd \(V-7\). This list is updated quarterly.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 318.0 Td (2.3 Obligation to Use Preferred Vendors) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 302.0 Td (For all standard catalogue materials with an estimated purchase value above) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 286.0 Td ($1,000, procurement staff must select a preferred vendor. Use of a non-preferred) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 270.0 Td (vendor for orders above $1,000 requires written justification and manager) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 254.0 Td (approval, regardless of the order amount.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 230.0 Td (2.4 Preferred Vendor Auto-Approval Benefit) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 214.0 Td (Purchase requisitions below $5,000 placed with a preferred vendor are eligible) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 198.0 Td (for auto-approval under POL-PROC-001 Section 2.1. This benefit does not apply to) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 182.0 Td (non-preferred vendors.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 158.0 Td (3. NON-PREFERRED VENDOR USE) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 134.0 Td (3.1 Justification Required) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 118.0 Td (When a preferred vendor cannot fulfil a requirement \(due to stock-out, lead time) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 102.0 Td (constraints, or technical specification mismatch\), the requestor must document) Tj ET
endstream
