BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 720.0 Td (the reason and obtain manager approval before submitting a requisition against a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 704.0 Td (non-preferred vendor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 680.0 Td (3.2 One-Time Vendor Approval) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 664.0 Td (For emergency procurements from vendors not on the preferred list, a one-time) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 648.0 Td (vendor approval form must be submitted to the procurement team. Purchase orders) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 632.0 Td (may not be issued until the one-time approval is recorded in the system.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 608.0 Td (4. RESTRICTED VENDOR LIST) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 584.0 Td (4.1 Purpose) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 568.0 Td (The Restricted Vendor List \(RVL\) identifies vendors that are prohibited from) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 552.0 Td (receiving purchase orders due to compliance findings, sanctions, poor) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 536.0 Td (performance, or legal disputes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 512.0 Td (4.2 Enforcement) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 496.0 Td (The procurement system must automatically deny any purchase requisition naming an) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 480.0 Td (RVL vendor. No override is permitted at the system level; exceptions require) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 464.0 Td (written approval from the General Counsel and Chief Procurement Officer.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 440.0 Td (5. VENDOR PERFORMANCE REVIEW) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 424.0 Td (Preferred vendor status is reviewed quarterly. A vendor falling below 90% on-time) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 408.0 Td (delivery over two consecutive quarters is placed on probationary status and may) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 392.0 Td (be removed from the preferred list.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 368.0 Td (6. PAYMENT TERMS) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 352.0 Td (All purchase orders issued to preferred vendors are subject to NET30 payment) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 336.0 Td (terms unless a specific framework agreement specifies otherwise. Non-preferred) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 320.0 Td (vendors are subject to NET45 terms.) Tj ET
